reut2-012.sgm, CITIC TO ISSUE 30 BILLION YEN BOND IN TOKYO, The China International Trust andInvestment Corp (CITIC) will issue a 30 billion yen, 10-yearbond on April 23, Daiwa Securities said as lead manager.    The samurai bond, to be signed on on April 14, will be thefirst since an Asian Development Bank issue in February.    The coupon is expected to be around five pct, Daiwa said.    The April Japanese government 10-year bond coupon has beenset at 4.7 pct against five pct on the March bond. REUTER&#3;
